e Test! Get Certified!: Exam FC0-U71, 2nd Edition&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#cccertifiedincybersecuritystudyguide"&gt;CC Certified in Cybersecurity Study Guide&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#ccnacertificationstudyguidevolume1_exam200-301v112ndedition"&gt;CCNA Certification Study Guide Volume 1: Exam 200-301 v1.1, 2nd Edition&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#bt18"&gt;Pay $18 or more to also unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#iappcipmcertifiedinformationprivacymanagerstudyguide"&gt;IAPP CIPM Certified Information Privacy Manager Study Guide&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#googlecloudcertifiedassociatecloudengineerstudyguide2ndedition"&gt;Google Cloud Certified Associate Cloud Engineer Study Guide, 2nd Edition&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#ccstciscocertifiedsupporttechnicianstudyguide_networkingexam"&gt;CCST Cisco Certified Support Technician Study Guide: Networking Exam&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#comptiacysapluspracticetests_examcs0-0033rdedition"&gt;CompTIA CySA+ Practice Tests: Exam CS0-003, 3rd Edition&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#awscertifiedcloudpractitionerstudyguidewith500practicetestquestion"&gt;AWS Certified Cloud Practitioner Study Guide With 500 Practice Test Questions: Foundational (CLF-C02) Exam, 2nd Edition&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#cehv12certifiedethicalhackerstudyguidewith750practicetestquestions"&gt;CEH v12 Certified Ethical Hacker Study Guide with 750 Practice Test Questions&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#lpisecurityessentialsstudyguide_exam020-100"&gt;LPI Security Essentials Study Guide: Exam 020-100&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#bt25"&gt;Pay $25 or more to also unlock!&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#comptianetworkplusstudyguide_examn10009_6thed"&gt;CompTIA Network+ Study Guide: Exam N10-009, 6th Edition&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#comptiasecuritypluspracticetestssy0701_3rded"&gt;CompTIA Security+ Practice Tests: Exam SY0-701, 3rd Edition&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#isc2cisspcertifiedinformationsystemssecurityprofessionalofficialpr"&gt;ISC2 CISSP Certified Information Systems Security Professional Official Practice Tests, 4th Edition&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#comptiapentestplusstudyguide_exampt0-003erdedition"&gt;CompTIA PenTest+ Study Guide: Exam PT0-003, 3rd Edition&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#awscertifiedadvancednetworkingofficialstudyguide_specialtyexam"&gt;AWS Certified Advanced Networking Study Guide: Specialty (ANS-C01) Exam, 2nd Edition&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#mcawindowsserverhybridadministratorcompletestudyguidewith400practi"&gt;MCA Windows Server Hybrid Administrator Complete Study Guide with 400 Practice Test Questions: Exam AZ-800 and Exam AZ-801&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="#ccnacertificationstudyguidevolume2_exam200-301"&gt;CCNA Certification Study Guide Volume 2: Exam 200-301 v1.1, 2nd Edition&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2 id="0"&gt;Pay $8 to unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="mca365modernadminstudyguide-md1012ndedition"&gt;&lt;a id="mca365modernadminstudyguide-md1012ndedition" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/mca365modernadminstudyguide-md1012ndedition_preview.pdf?t=st=1751246744~exp=1751333144~hmac=8369ac77d6130e91d1b8d5c916fd3f695c609694a1021be903167b48a3ef72df"&gt;MCA Microsoft 365 Certified Associate Modern Desktop Administrator Complete Study Guide with 900 Practice Test Questions: Exam MD-100 and Exam MD-101, 2nd Edition&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/071392c81e7b89d365f6e653093d2111a979154b.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=7b180d73603328f5a80c01c025d11695"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;The All-in-One COMPLETE Study Guide to help you prepare for earning the MCA Modern Desktop Administrator certification!In the MCA Modern Desktop Administrator Complete Study Guide: Exam MD-100 and Exam MD-101, Second Edition, well-known Windows guru and 5-time Microsoft MVP, William Panek, guides you through the UPDATED Exam MD-100, Windows Client, and UPDATED Exam MD-101, Managing Modern Desktops. He covers 100% of the objectives, providing real world scenarios, hands-on exercises, and challenging review questions. He also dives deeper into some of the more complex topics and technologies, including the following:    Deploy Windows  Manage devices and data  Configure storage and connectivity  Maintain Windows  Deploy and upgrade operating systems  Manage policies and profiles  Manage and protect devices  Manage apps and data    With this Study Guide, you also get access to Sybex's superior online learning environment with an Assessment Test, Bonus Practice Exams, Flashcards, Searchable Glossary, and Videos for many of the chapter exercises.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="comptiaapluscertmike_preparepracticepassthetestgetcertified_core1e"&gt;&lt;a id="comptiaapluscertmike_preparepracticepassthetestgetcertified_core1e" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/comptiaapluscertmike_preparepracticepassthetestgetcertified_core1e_preview.pdf?t=st=1751246744~exp=1751333144~hmac=b2a0edf2793815663ab8da949f89d54427c16b0983c04a796fcd1f6bf71ae899"&gt;CompTIA A+ CertMike: Prepare. Practice. Pass the Test! Get Certified!: Core 1 Exam 220-1101&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/f0c7b59774d086f8a2ccd111cec777fbdaf3a93f.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=7985e71e3972860509aa945fd018564f"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Let CertMike help you prepare, practice, and pass the CompTIA A+ Core 1 exam!   Sybex's NEW CompTIA A+ CertMike: Prepare. Practice. Pass the Test! Get Certified! Core 1 Exam 220-1101 lets you skip the fluff and focus only on the material you need to understand for passing CompTIA A+ Core 1 Exam 220-1101--and working towards earning your certification! Ace the test using the proven CertMike approach:    Prepare  As your personal study coach, CertMike guides you through all the exam objectives, helping you gain an understanding of important topics and how they apply to on-the-job scenarios!  Practice  Each chapter includes two multiple choice practice questions. Work through the detailed explanations to evaluate each answer option and understand the reason for the best answer.  Pass  On exam day, take the critical knowledge youve learned into the test. Youll feel ready and confident to pass the exam and earn your certification!     The CompTIA A+ certification validates you have the knowledge and skills required to install, configure, and maintain computer equipment, mobile devices, and software for end users; service components based on customer requirements; understand networking basics and apply basic cybersecurity methods to mitigate threats; properly and safely diagnose, resolve, and document common hardware and software issues; apply troubleshooting skills and provide customer support using appropriate communication skills; and understand the basics of scripting, cloud technologies, virtualization, and multi-OS deployments in corporate environments.  Readers also have access to additional online study tools, including a bonus practice exam and audio recordings of the books Exam Essentials to help you review for the actual exam. Prepare smarter with Sybex's NEW CertMike Get Certified! for achieving the CompTIA A+ certification!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="comptiaapluscertmike_preparepracticepassthetestgetcertified_core2e"&gt;&lt;a id="comptiaapluscertmike_preparepracticepassthetestgetcertified_core2e" href="https://cdn.humble.com/humblebundle/ops/pdfs/comptiaapluscertmike_preparepracticepassthetestgetcertified_core2e_preview.pdf?t=st=1751246744~exp=1751333144~hmac=453f6779bea247060ce3bb02f9a48267b0dfc3a8718ad40736906079550e8f9c"&gt;CompTIA A+ CertMike: Prepare. Practice. Pass the Test! Get Certified!: Core 2 