;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=87fa66006ee66483dfbdd5dcb75493a0"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;This project includes everything pictured, including all assets, maps, and Materials created in the Unreal Engine. Each asset was created for realistic AAA-quality visuals, style, and budget.Technical details&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Throttle can be controlled by W key and S key&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Steer can be controlled by A key and D key&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Camera Rotation can be controlled by Mouse&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Materials are changeable in Detail Panel&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Setup for easy drop and play&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Custom sounds&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Master Material to control features&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Multiple Design Skins&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Includes Static Mesh Version&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;2K and 4K Texture Sets&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Master material setup that control shader looks&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Additional controls for roughness, albedo, normals and more&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Channel packed Roughness | Metalness | Ambient Occlusion&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Optimized for games&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Free of all legal issues as all branding and labels are custom made by our studio&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Fully detailed models from all sides&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Includes test dynamic lighting scene&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;Number of Blueprints: 1&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Input: See above&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Network Replicated: No&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Supported Development Platforms: All&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Windows: Yes&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Mac: Yes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="sfxcyberpunk"&gt;&lt;a id="sfxcyberpunk" href="https://youtu.be/K1bhBMdqWq0"&gt;SFX Cyberpunk&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/54d5293ed9ca7376c5cb1fd91cc39acea90b0c44.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=75b889d5b7aeec7511da305f0e5a7546"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Cyberpunk Themed Sound Effect Pack&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="zbrush_beginnertoadvancedcourseonthreeminiatures"&gt;&lt;a id="zbrush_beginnertoadvancedcourseonthreeminiatures" href="https://youtu.be/F_9JzAHvNKM"&gt;ZBrush: Beginner to Advanced Course on Three Miniatures&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Step into the world of ZBrush as you embark on a journey to craft three miniature figures . Our Udemy course is your ticket to mastering the sculpting, material, and landscapes. Our instructor from Brazil, Celito Moura, has been working in the cinema industry since 2003 as a 3D artist, concept artist, storyboardist, texture artist, and art director. His clientele includes Cartoon Network, Napster, Banco do Brasil, and many others. Currently he is focused on the area of miniatures and collectibles. With his experience, this course is tailored for from beginners and experienced artists. You’ll start by gaining a solid foundation in the principles of sculpting, clothing and anatomy. Throughout the course, you’ll engage in a practical project designed to sharpen your skills and deepen your understanding of the creative process. By the end, you’ll emerge with a portfolio-worthy environment, ready to showcase your talent and impress potential employers. Key topics include: Understanding the principles of sculpting Navigating ZBrush’s robust toolset and features Using and creating brushes Posing, finalizing, and optimizing your models for rendering Exporting your miniature for production Taking renders on Blender and Photoshop Whether you’re an enthusiast looking to break into the gaming industry or a professional seeking to refine your craft, this course offers invaluable insights and practical skills to elevate your character art.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="vfxsmokeunrealengine"&gt;&lt;a id="vfxsmokeunrealengine"&gt;VFX Smoke (Unreal Engine)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/8d411e214c9871fd2e6e66cf32e75c88691f630c.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=a164cdab56e0312406c156a83c8814fe"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Leartes Presents Awesome VFX Pack:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Unreal Engine Version: 5.0&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;The Smoke VFX Packs include:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Fog&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;SmokeChimney&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;SmokeToxic&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="watervfxunrealengine"&gt;&lt;a id="watervfxunrealengine"&gt;Water VFX (Unreal Engine)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/54c4491f580d50c4b8496c6c5e8ae03fd6afe880.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=ef87b1f59345c54c34e6df07c09fa568"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Leartes Presents Awesome VFX Pack:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Unreal Engine Version: 5.0&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;The Water VFX Packs include:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Heavy Rain&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Light Rain&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Snow&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Water Dripple&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Waterfall&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Water Flow&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Water fountain&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Water Leak&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="objectdistributiontoolunrealenginetoolplugin"&gt;&lt;a id="objectdistributiontoolunrealenginetoolplugin" href="https://youtu.be/qWYrB-D7W1g"&gt;Object Distribution Tool (Unreal Engine)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/07173d4d7724dfb57cdf15d95bbfff96e5ed8e40.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=0f4397b150d22f00785a74fdf3f940c6"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Welcome to the innovative world of Leartes Studios, where passion for gaming meets Unreal Engine’s automation possibilities. Leartes Studios is dedicated to pushing the boundaries of being a leading art outsourcing company.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Quick access to the tool interface with a custom tool menu&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;The customizable window for personal uses&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Allows you to automatically create a preset from the selected assets in the Content Browser.&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;A new parameter called ""Spawn Density"" has been added, which allows bulk adjustment of object counts quantities in a specified proportion, enabling easy increase or decrease of object placements.&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;No custom class dependencies can be removed from the project at any time&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Create and simulate an unlimited number of different mesh types in various arrangements.&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Save and reuse builds you created using presets&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Combine your presets with Mixer to instantly create more complex structures.&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;Code Modules ObjectDistribution(Editor)&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;ObjectDistributionManger(Editor)&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Number Of C++ Classes: 21&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Number of Blueprints: 1&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Network Replicated: No&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Supported Development Platforms: Win64&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Supported Target Build Platforms: Win64&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="500plusfantasyiconsunity"&gt;&lt;a id="500plusfantasyiconsunity"&gt;500+ Fantasy Icons&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/2a48efa76b2762883b425eaba75028432715aa29.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=6c32c834ea4f50953032e5a1a96223cb"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Fantasy RPG Icons (500+)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This pack includes highly detailed icons that will be useful for those who create RPG games.FULL PACK CONTENT:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Background and No Background version for ALL Icons!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Each icon is 1080x1080 pixels (PNG)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Weapons:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;44x Axes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;40x Daggers&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;47x Shields&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;39x Swords&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Clothings:&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;35x Armors&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;31x Boots&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;28x Helmets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;16x Necklaces&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;16x Pants&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Items:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;29x Books&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;17x Foods&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;60x Gems&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;44x Loots&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;18x Potions&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;40x Skills&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h3 id="cosmosonemonthfreesubscription"&gt;&lt;a id="cosmosonemonthfreesubscription"&gt;Cosmos One Month Free Subscription&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/82a087ffcb2d3ad5202bfffab5e93e16f56c72a9.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=4bbccd4daab6a15615f88e28eeb1c172"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Ignite Your Creativity With Our Premium 3D Assets&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Unleash your creative potential and bring your imagination to life like never before with our extensive selection of high-quality 3D assets.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Unlocks the 1000+ Props&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://cosmos.leartesstudios.com/assets"&gt;https://cosmos.leartesstudios.com/assets&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="cosmos50discountcode"&gt;&lt;a id="cosmos50discountcode"&gt;Cosmos 50% Discount Code&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/a986d343c83517a50cb2456760619802a9d37937.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=9194715502a4f92d422ce7985a0f6514"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;50% Discount code valid for all Leartes Studios Products -&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://cosmos.leartesstudios.com/"&gt;https://cosmos.leartesstudios.com/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Valid only for products that are not currently part of an active sale.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Some products may be excluded, such as time-limited deals, bundles, or assets from publishers other than&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Leartes Studios&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;and&lt;span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;StylArts&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;The Redemption period only valid for 3 month&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 id="bt10"&gt;Pay $10 or more to also unlock!&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id="ultimatelightingandcameratoolulct"&gt;&lt;a id="ultimatelightingandcameratoolulct" href="https://youtu.be/fHjMEjKszUE"&gt;Ultimate Lighting and Camera Tool ( ULCT )&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img src="https://hb.imgix.net/8320df06738a0a6e0da4ad64f438e946a5b2feae.jpg?auto=compress,format&amp;fit=clip&amp;h=350&amp;w=600&amp;s=2ca150067eb0fbc272ee0770eceecc49"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Welcome to the innovative world of Leartes Studios, where passion for gaming meets Unreal Engine’s automation possibilities.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;We have developed a new tool for the gaming community: The Ultimate Lighting and Camera Tool, which accelerates and simplifies your Unreal Engine lighting and camera workflow.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Technical details&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Create custom lights converting them each other easily&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Apply custom light masks to the lights&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Creating light sensor interacting with characters&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Automatically adjust lightmap densities for certain meshes on the scene or asset's settings&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;The HDRI Backdrop Manager It creates easy setup for HDRI's&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Quick access the project settings in terms of the lighting main setup&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;Code Modules:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;LightingTool(Editor)&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;LightingGame(Runtime)&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;Number Of C++ Classes:&amp;nbsp;28&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Number of Blueprints:&amp;nbsp;16&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Network Replicated:&amp;nbsp;No&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Supported Development Platforms: Win64&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Supported Target Build Platforms: Win64&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="feudaljapanesecastle"&gt;&lt;a id="feudaljapanesecastle" href="https://youtu.be/-h0S4hhYNZ8"&gt;Feudal Japanese Castle&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Feudal Japanese Castle Environment with 197 Unique Meshes. Including all showcased assets, and high-quality assets. With a good level of detail and optimized for Game Ready Projects.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Technical details&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;197 Unique Meshes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Attention to Detail / AAA Quality&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Controllable parameters in Material Instances&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High-Quality Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Game ready/Optimized&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Unique Concepts of Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High Attention to Details&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Material Variations For Some Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Texture Sizes:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;4096&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;2048&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;1024&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Texture Size: 4096 for detailed Assets, 2048 for Mid-sized Assets, &amp;amp; 1024 for small assets&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Collision: Yes, Custom collisions for complex assets&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;LODs: Yes, 4 LODs for complex assets&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Meshes: 197 Unique Meshes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Materials and Material Instances: 130&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Textures: 205&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Development Platforms: All Platforms&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Development Versions: Unreal Engine 5.0, 5.1, 5.2, 5.3, 5.4, 5.5+&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="stylizeddesertbazaar"&gt;&lt;a id="stylizeddesertbazaar" href="https://youtu.be/HEleNaeiH3U"&gt;Stylized Desert Bazaar&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Stylized Desert Bazaar Environment with 106 Assets. There are many different types of Assets to help you create or polish your Environments. All Assets made with unique concepts and Showcased Example levels are also included in the Project.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Technical details&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;High Attention to Details&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Unique Concepts of Assets&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;High-Quality Assets&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Game-ready / Optimized&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;p&gt;Number of Unique Meshes: 106&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;Collision: Yes&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&g