 many assets and materials, including levels. The building meshes are modular and fit in a 50cm grid. It is a great package to create or populate your game levels.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;High Quality / Big Pack&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Over 250 Unique Meshes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;13 Decals&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;A lot of HQ Props&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Example Map / Overview Map&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Unique Meshes: 257&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Collision: Yes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;LODs: Yes up to 4&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Materials and Material Instances: 183&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Blueprints : 27&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Number of Textures: 423&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Texture Resolutions: 1K , 2K&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Development Platforms:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Windows: Yes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Mac: Yes&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Supported Engine Versions : 4.22 , 4.23 , 4.24 , 4.25 , 4.26 , 4.27+ , UE5 , 5.1 , 5.2 , 5.3 , 5.4 , 5.5+&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="japanesetemple"&gt;&lt;a id="japanesetemple" href="https://youtu.be/SVtgD_o4gBc"&gt;Japanese Temple&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Imagine a Japanese temple with a massive wooden structure. Inside the temple, you will feel small. The project includes many ready-to-use braziers, candles, and sculptures.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Japanese Temple Environment with 140+ Unique Meshes. Including all showcased assets, and high-quality assets. With a good level of detail and optimized for Game Ready Projects.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Features:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;148 Unique Meshes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Attention to Detail / AAA Quality&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Controllable parameters in Material Instances&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High-Quality Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Game ready/Optimized&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Unique Concepts of Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;High Attention to Detail&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Material Variations For Some Assets&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Texture Sizes:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&