e Games&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Unreal Engine Version: 5.0&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="creatinganindustrialconceptartinblenderandphotoshop"&gt;&lt;a id="creatinganindustrialconceptartinblenderandphotoshop" href="https://youtu.be/23_tf9jT4lM"&gt;Creating an Industrial Concept Art in Blender / Photoshop&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;img&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Step into the world of Unreal Engine 5 as you embark on a journey to craft an abandoned church environment and level art in Unreal Engine 5. Our Udemy course is your ticket to mastering the 3D level art , lighting , set dressing and creating landscapes. Led by the seasoned industry professional, Louis Lin, this course is tailored for both beginners and experienced artists alike. You’ll start by gaining a solid foundation in the principles of level artistry, learning how to execute your vision with precision. Throughout the course, you’ll engage in a practical project designed to sharpen your skills and deepen your understanding of the creative process. By the end, you’ll emerge with a portfolio-worthy environment, ready to showcase your talent and impress potential employers. Key topics include: Understanding the principles of level artistry and environmental design Navigating Unreal Engine 5’s robust toolset and features Implementing dynamic lighting and atmospheric effects to enhance realism Incorporating storytelling elements to create an immersive experience Taking cinematic renders with the help of Cine Camera Actor Implementing post process volumes for color correction Using DaVinci Resolve for color grading and final touches Whether you’re an enthusiast looking to break into the gaming industry or a professional seeking to refine your craft, this course offers invaluable insights and practical skills to elevate your level art.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 id="creatingabandonedchurch3denvironmentinunrealengine5"&gt;&lt;a id="creatingabandonedchurch3denvironmentinunrealengine5" href="https://youtu.be/tlaxdn6tJGY"&gt;Creating Aband